When I delete screen with name updateJIT002Screen and verify
When I add new screen with name JIT002Screen

When I close the modal popup

When I close the modal popup

Then I should see slider message with content "Updated screen successfully"
Then I should see the screen with name updateJIT002Screen display in list Pages
